<h2>securitymastod.one</h2>
<p>An open Mastodon instance for information security pros and enthusiasts. Donate to hosting expenses at <a href="https://paypal.me/securitymastodon">PayPal</a> or <a href="https://www.patreon.com/securitymastodon">Patreon</a>
