<div class='panel'><p>Donate to hosting expenses at <a href="https://paypal.me/securitymastodon">PayPal</a> or <a href="https://www.patreon.com/securitymastodon">Patreon</a> Hosting expenses are currently on a special; $63.99 total per year on an OpenVZ hosting provider. (This introductory price will probably not last, but a year is forever in internet time...) However, we have frequently experienced downtime due to hosting provider issues such as running into simultaneous connection limits, etc. The goal of asking for donations is to get $370/year to upgrade to a KVM VPS or dedicated server on a more stable hosting provider.</p>

<p>This site is run by <a href="https://securitymastod.one/@scriptjunkie">@scriptjunkie</a></p></div>
